[size=4][b]What[/b][/size]

[size=3]Raises the multiplayer lobby cap from the vanilla 8 to 100. The lobby slider just goes higher — everything else about hosting and joining stays the same.[/size]

[list]
[*][size=3][b]Lobby cap raised to 100[/b] — the vanilla slider only goes up to 8 players; this mod extends it. Set whatever cap you actually want; the new ceiling is 100.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Last-used count remembered[/b] — once you set a lobby size, the host UI defaults to that value next session instead of resetting to vanilla.[/size]
[*][size=3][b]Host-side cap[/b] — the mod is what raises the slider, so the host needs it installed. Joining clients will need whatever else the host has installed, same as any modded lobby.[/size]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Other mods of mine you might like[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/224]More Jewelry[/url] — six extra jewelry slots — pairs nicely if your big lobby is stat-stacking for end-game stuff.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/205]More Scythes Redux[/url] — adds four new craftable scythes; enough scythes to go around for a full lobby.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/37]Easy Living[/url] — a grab-bag of QoL tweaks that scale well across multiple players in one save.[/size]
[*][size=3][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/31]Keep Alive[/url] — required by this mod; keeps everything loaded between play sessions.[/size]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Configuration[/b][/size]

[size=3]If you installed the required [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/30]Sun Haven BepInEx Pack[/url] and this mod is configurable, press F1 in-game to open the config interface.[/size]

[size=4][b]Requirements[/b][/size]

[list]
[*][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/30][size=3]Sun Haven BepInEx Pack[/size][/url]
[*][url=https://www.nexusmods.com/sunhaven/mods/31][size=3]Keep Alive[/size][/url]
[/list]

[size=4][b]Compatibility[/b][/size]

[size=3]Built and tested against the latest Steam build of Sun Haven.[/size]

[size=4][b]Installation[/b][/size]

[size=3]Installation using Vortex is the recommended installation method. If you wish to install manually, extract the contents of the mod archive into:

[code]...&#92;steamapps&#92;common&#92;Sun Haven&#92;BepInEx&#92;plugins[/code][/size]

